snippet.title: Disney Channel Animation
snippet.description:
Welcome to Disney Channel Animation – your home for bold characters, big laughs, and the most animated adventures around! From the inventions of Phineas and Ferb to the everyday chaos of Big City Greens, the wild adventures of StuGo, the heartfelt moments of Kiff and beyond,  this is your animated escape into worlds where anything can happen (and probably will)!
 
Expect new episodes, clips, songs, and surprises every week – all from the shows you love and the ones you’re about to discover!

Keep up with our new videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiv1IUQDVSNKSwiTLE-l6pwhnu75gRIfH
